quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,217,"Kí o sì gbáralé Alágbára, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run;"
  26,218,"Ẹni tó ń rí ọ nígbà tí ò ń dìde nàró (fún ìrun kíkí)"
  26,219,"àti ìyírapadà rẹ (fún rukuu àti ìforíkanlẹ̀) láààrin àwọn olùforíkanlẹ̀."
  33,70,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, ẹ bẹ̀rù Allāhu. Kí ẹ sì sọ ọ̀rọ̀ déédé."
  33,71,"(Allāhu) máa ṣàtúnṣe àwọn iṣẹ́ yín fún yín, Ó sì máa ṣàforíjìn àwọn ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ yín fún yín. Àti pé ẹni tí ó bá tẹ̀lé ti Allāhu àti Òjíṣẹ́ Rẹ̀, ó kúkú ti jèrè ní èrèǹjẹ ńlá."
  33,72,"Dájúdájú Àwa fi àgbàfipamọ́ (iṣẹ́ ẹ̀sìn àṣegbaláádá) lọ àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ àti àpáta. Wọ́n kọ̀ láti gbé e; wọ́n páyà rẹ̀. Ènìyàn sì gbé e. Dájúdájú (ènìyàn) jẹ́ alábòsí, aláìmọ̀kan.{1}.",1:[Àgbàfipamọ́ ni ìtúmọ̀ “ ’amọ̄nah”. Èyí sì túmọ̀ sí ohun tí wọ́n gbé lé wa lọ́wọ́ fún ṣíṣọ́ àti àmójútó. Ohun tí Allāhu - tó ga jùlọ - gbélé wa lọ́wọ́ tí a óò máa ṣọ́, tí a óò máa ṣe àmójútó rẹ̀ títí di ọjọ́ ikú ẹnì kọ̀ọ̀kan wa ni ẹ̀sìn Rẹ̀, ’Islām. Allāhu sì gbé ẹ̀sìn náà kalẹ̀ pẹ̀lú ẹ̀san.]
  34,49,"Sọ pé: “Òdodo ti dé. Irọ́ (aṣ-ṣaetọ̄n) kò lè mú n̄ǹkan bẹ, kò sì lè dá n̄ǹkan padà (lẹ́yìn tó ti kú).”"
  34,50,"Sọ pé: “Tí mo bá ṣìnà, mo ṣìnà fún ẹ̀mí ara mi ni. Tí mo bá sì mọ̀nà, nípa ohun tí Olúwa mi fi ránṣẹ́ sì mi ní ìmísí ni. Dájúdájú Òun ni Olùgbọ́, Alásùn-únmọ́ ẹ̀dá.”{1}.",1:[Okùnfà āyah yìí ni pé, àwọn ọ̀ṣẹbọ ìlú Mọkkah ń sọ fún Ànábì Muhammad - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - pé, “Tí o bá fi lè pa ẹ̀sìn ìbọ̀rìṣà àwọn bàbá rẹ tì, o ti ṣìnà nìyẹn.” Allāhu sì sọ āyah kalẹ̀.]
  34,51,"Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé o lè rí (ẹ̀sín wọn ni) nígbà tí ẹ̀rù bá dé bá wọn (ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde, o máa rí i pé), kò níí sí ìmóríbọ́ kan (fún wọn). A sì máa gbá wọn mú láti àyè tó súnmọ́."
  35,34,"Wọ́n yóò sọ pé: “Gbogbo ẹyìn ń jẹ́ ti Allāhu, Ẹni tí Ó mú ìbànújẹ́ kúrò fún wa. Dájúdájú Olúwa wa ni Aláforíjìn, Ọlọ́pẹ́,{1}.",1:[Nínú orúkọ àti ìròyìn Allāhu ni “Ṣākir” àti “Ṣakūr”.]
  35,35,"Ẹni tí Ó sọ̀ wá kalẹ̀ sínú ibùgbé gbére nínú oore àjùlọ Rẹ̀. Wàhálà kan kò níí kàn wá nínú rẹ̀. Ìkáàárẹ̀ kan kò sì níí bá wa nínú rẹ̀."
  35,36,"Àti pé àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́, iná Jahanamọ ń bẹ fún wọn. A ò níí pa wọ́n (sínú rẹ̀), áḿbọ̀sìbọ́sí pé wọ́n yóò kú. A ò níí ṣe ìyà inú rẹ̀ ní fífúyẹ́ fún wọn. Báyẹn ni A ṣe ń san gbogbo àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ ní ẹ̀san."
  36,19,"Wọ́n sọ pé: “Àmì aburú yín ń bẹ pẹ̀lú yín. Ṣé nítorí pé wọ́n ṣe ìṣítí fún yín (l’ẹ fi rí àmì aburú lára wa)? Kò rí bẹ́ẹ̀! Ìjọ alákọyọ ni yín ni.”"
  36,20,"Ọkùnrin kan sáré dé láti òpin ìlú náà, ó wí pé: “Ẹ̀yin ènìyàn mi, ẹ tẹ̀lé àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ náà."
  36,21,"Ẹ tẹ̀lé ẹni tí kò bèèrè owó-ọ̀yà kan ní ọwọ́ yín. Olùmọ̀nà sì ni wọ́n."
  37,4,"Dájúdájú ọ̀kan ṣoṣo ni Ọlọ́hun yín tí ẹ gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo."
  37,5,"Olúwa àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ àti ohunkóhun tí ń bẹ láààrin àwọn méjèèjì. Òun sì ni Olúwa àwọn ibùyọ òòrùn."
  37,6,"Dájúdájú Àwa fi àwọn ìràwọ̀ ṣe sánmọ̀ ilé ayé ní ọ̀ṣọ́"